OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPersistent
OL,6,Frain, locally heavy in places, through
OL,7,Fthe evening. This clearing all but far
OL,8,Feastern coasts by dawn, with dry
OL,9,Fconditions and occasional clear spells
OL,10,Ffollowing. Generally milder than
OL,11,Fprevious nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FGenerally a dry and bright
OL,14,Fstart, rain across far eastern coasts
OL,15,Fsoon clearing. Isolated afternoon
OL,16,Fshowers in the far west spread east
OL,17,Finto the evening, becoming heavy in
OL,18,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
